item.title: CVE-2023-0983|2023-04-10T13:17:58.149Z -- unknown -- stylish%20cost%20calculator%20premium
item.description: The stylish-cost-calculator-premium WordPress plugin before 7.9.0 does not sanitise and escape a parameter before outputting it back in the page, leading to a Stored Cross-Site Scripting which could be used against admins when viewing submissions submitted through the Email Quote Form.
